36 SECTION 5.4. The initial appointments to the governing board of the Lake Norman
37 Marine Commission will become effective on the date that is seven calendar days following the
38 adoption by three or more eligible local governments of a joint resolution reconstituting the Lake
39 Norman Marine Commission.
40 SECTION 5.5. All rules, regulations, and decisions made by the predecessor Lake
41 Norman Marine Commission, reconstituted in accordance with this Part, shall remain in full force
42 and effect until and unless duly modified by the successor entity.
